generic:link.msg:message: Identity "Value of Total of Share Capital and Free Reserves = (Ordinary Shares, Preference shares to be compulsorily convertible into equity, Perpetual Debt Instrument and Free Reserves)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Total of deduction to the equity capital = (Accumulated balance of loss + Deferred Revenue Expenditure + Deferred Tax Asset (Net) + Other Intangible Assets + Others)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Owned Funds = (Total of common equity capital - Total of deductions to equity capital)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total adjustments to calculate net owned funds = (Total of Total investment in shares of (Subsidiaries, Wholly-Owned Subsidiary/JV abroad, Companies in the same Group, Other non-banking financial companies)) + Total of the book value of debentures, bonds, outstanding loans and advances, bills purchased and discounted (including hire-purchase and lease finance) made to, and deposits with (Subsidiaries, Wholly-Owned Subsidiary/JV abroad, Companies in the same Group)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Amount of item (xiii) in excess of 10% of item (x) above = (Max (Total Adjustments to Calculate Net Owned Funds - (0.1*Owned Funds); Else Value of Amount of item (xiii) in excess of 10% of item (x) above = Total Adjustments to Calculate Net Owned Funds, if Owned Funds < 0 \)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Net Owned Funds = (Owned Fund - Amount of item (xiii) in excess of 10% of item (x) above); Else Value of Net Owned Funds = Owned Fund - Total, If Owned Fund < 0)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Total shareholding pattern = (Central Govt. + State Govt. + Banks, Fis, Insurance Cos. + FDIs + Mutual Funds + Corporates + Public + Indian Promoters + Others)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Appreciation in the book value of quoted investment and equity share capital = (50% of the unrealized appreciation in the book value of quoted investments as at the date of last audited Balance sheet + Increase if any, in the equity share capital since the date of the last audited balance sheet)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Adjusted Net Worth = (Owned Fund + Total of Appreciation in the book value of quoted investments & equity share capital - Diminution in the aggregate book value of quoted investments - Reduction, if any, in the equity share capital since the date of the last audited balance sheet)" do not tally

Identity "Value of Adjusted Networth to RWA = ((Adjusted Net Worth) / (Adjusted value of Total Weighted Assets i.e. on-balance sheet items + Adjusted Value of Total non-funded exposure))" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Aggregate Tier II Capital = (Preference Share Capital other than those compulsorily convertible into equity + Cumulative Convertible Preference Shares + Revaluation reserves (At Discount rate of 55%) + General provisions and loss reserves including Provisions for Standard Assets (to the extent not attributable to actual diminution in value or identifiable potential loss in any specific asset and are available to meet unexpected losses, to the extent of 1.25% of RWA) + Hybrid debt capital instruments + Subordinated debt(Subjected to prescribed Discount Rates & Not exceeding 50% of Tier I) + Others ( to be specified in remarks column) - First Loss Credit Enhancement)" do not tally.
Value of Total Capital Funds should be taken from the prescribed formula.
Identity "Value of Total risk weighted assets/ exposures = (Adjusted value of funded risk assets i.e. on-balance sheet items + Adjusted value of non-funded and off-balance sheet items)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Risk exposure to Tier II capital = (Aggregate Tier II Capital/ Total risk weighted assets/ exposures, if Total risk weighted assets/ exposures > 0)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Risk exposure to Tier II capital = (Total Capital Funds/ Total risk weighted assets/ exposures, if Total risk weighted assets/ exposures > 0)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total deposits = (Deposits received from public in the form of Fixed Deposits, Recurring Deposits etc + Deposits received from shareholders by a Public Limited Company (other than Nidhis) + Money received by issue of Non-convertible unsecured debentures + Any other type of public deposits + Interest accrued on the above)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Unencumbered approved securities = (Central Government'+ State Government)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Total 2(a) + 2(b) - Unencumbered approved securities = (Central Government'+ State Government + Deposits in scheduled commercial banks)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Public Deposits outstanding as on date of this return (i.e. last working day of the quarter to which this return relates) = (PD outstanding + Interest accrued but not due)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Equivalent Value = (Book Value*Conversion Factor)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = Equivalent Value*Risk Weight" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Sub-total = (Bonds of public sector banks - Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Bonds of public sector banks - Amounts not deducted in PART 1 + FDs/CDs/bonds of public financial institutions - Amounts deducted in PART 1 + FDs/CDs/bonds of public financial institutions - Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Shares of all companies and debentures/ bonds/ commercial papers of companies and units of all mutual funds = (Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Stock on hire = (Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Inter-corporate loans/ deposits = (Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Sub-total of other secured loans and advances considered good = (Loans and advances fully secured against deposits held + Loans to staff + Amounts deducted in institutions - Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Bills purchased/ discounted = (Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Assets leased out = (Amounts deducted in PART 1 + Amounts not deducted in PART 1)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total credit exposure = (Sub-Totals of (Current Assets + Inter-corporate loans/ deposits + Other secured loans and advances considered good + Bills Purchased/ discounted + Others + Fixed Assets))" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total Weighted Assets = (Cash + Bank balances including fixed deposits & certificates of deposits + The deposits/collateral kept with CCIL in connection with CBLO + Approved securities as defined in Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 + Sub-total of FDs/CDs/bonds of public financial institutions + Total credit exposure + Premises + Furniture & Fixtures + Income-tax deducted at source (net of Provisions) + Advance tax paid (net of Provision) + Interest due on Government securities + Others (to be specified in Table 8: Other Assets) + Fund-based claims on the Central Government + Direct loan / credit / overdraft exposure and investment in State Government securities + Central Government guaranteed claims + State Government guaranteed claims, which have not remained in default / which are in default for a period not more than 90 days + State Government guaranteed claims which have remained in default for a period of more than 90 days)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for cash" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for Bank balances including fixed deposits & certificates of deposits" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for the deposits/collateral kept with CCIL in connection with CBLO" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for investments" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for current assets" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for fixed assets net of depreciation" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for other current assets" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for approved securities as defined in Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Prescribed amount of Liquid Assets required to be maintained at "15%" of public deposits = (15% *Total ( 1+2+3(i)+3(ii)+4))" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Demand for Penal Interest made by RBI should be reported if SLR was not complied in previous quarter.
Reporting of "Penal Charges should be mandatory.

Identity "Value of Total Adjusted Value = (Cash + Bank balances including fixed deposits & certificates of deposits + The deposits/collateral kept with CCIL in connection with CBLO + Approved securities as defined in Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 + Sub-total of FDs/CDs/bonds of public financial institutions + Total credit exposure + Premises + Furniture & Fixtures + Income-tax deducted at source (net of Provisions) + Advance tax paid (net of Provision) + Interest due on Government securities + Others (to be specified in Table 8: Other Assets) + Fund-based claims on the Central Government + Direct loan / credit / overdraft exposure and investment in State Government securities + Central Government guaranteed claims + State Government guaranteed claims, which have not remained in default / which are in default for a period not more than 90 days + State Government guaranteed claims which have remained in default for a period of more than 90 days)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Current Assets = Value of all Current Assets of all companies)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Other Assets = Value of all Other Assets of all companies)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for domestic sovereign" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Risk exposure to Tier I capital = (Net owned fund/ Total risk weighted assets/ exposures, if Total risk weighted assets/ exposures > 0)" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted Value = (Book Value*Risk Weight) for other assets" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Owned Funds = (Total of common equity capital - Total of deductions to equity capital) for Core Investment Companies" do not tally.
Identity "Value of Adjusted value of non-funded and off-balance sheet items = (Total non-funded exposures adjusted Value in Sheet Part 4)" do not tally.

Identity "Value of Total of Share Capital and Free Reserves = (Ordinary Shares, Preference shares to be compulsorily convertible into equity, Perpetual Debt Instrument and Free Reserves) for Core Investment Companies" do not tally.
PAN should be in valid format. Else, Value of PAN should be NA.
